title: Medieval 2 Total War Online Battle #202 (2vs2) - Realism Tournament Game 1
description:
Hey guys in this battle Emperor of The Great Unknown and I watch an old battle from a tournament that never finished.  The rules are realism and they make quite the battles.  This is game 1.  There are 3 total! Enjoy :D 

Check out Emperor's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCLwA3MWOX4RjrhxUUHcoOqw

Realism Rules: 12K money each player
Max 6 Elite Units, 10 hired units, no musketeers, and max 2 art

Swissman15: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClk-5xVdzgEoXxS4vFjQ5SA

Captain Invisible: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsB6k6OrSNGAEpOK8qMF_Cg


Follow me on twitter: https://twitter.com/pixelatedapollo
